text: Cumia alfredensis, common name : the narrow dwarf triton, is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Colubrariidae. ==Description== The shell size varies between 20 mm and 50 mm ==Distribution== It is distributed along KwaZuluNatal, South Africa ==References== ==External links== * Category:Colubrariidae Category:Gastropods described in 1915
title: Cumia alfredensis
